---
interface Props {
    city?: string;
}

const { city = "sua localização" } = Astro.props;
---
<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 relative z-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase mb-10 text-center text-white">Dúvidas Frequentes</h2>
    
    <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-[#1b1b1b] rounded overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer list-none focus:outline-none">
                <span class="font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-widest text-[#e2e2e2]">Quanto tempo demora?</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform text-brand-yellow" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400 text-sm">
                Nossa média de chegada em {city} é de 25 a 35 minutos, dependendo do tráfego local.
            </div>
        </details>
        
        <details class="group bg-[#1b1b1b] rounded overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer list-none focus:outline-none">
                <span class="font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-widest text-[#e2e2e2]">Quais formas de pagamento?</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform text-brand-yellow" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400 text-sm">
                Aceitamos Cartão de Crédito, Débito, PIX e dinheiro diretamente com o técnico no local.
            </div>
        </details>
        
        <details class="group bg-[#1b1b1b] rounded overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer list-none focus:outline-none">
                <span class="font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-widest text-[#e2e2e2]">Atendem em rodovias?</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform text-brand-yellow" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16.59 8.59L12 13.17 7.41 8.59 6 10l6 6 6-6z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400 text-sm">
                Sim, prestamos auxílio em todas as principais rodovias estaduais e federais da região metropolitana.
            </div>
        </details>
    </div>
</section>
